{s:5:\"title\";s:16:\"Community Events\";s:9:\"permalink\";s:126:\"http://tri.be/shop/wordpress-community-events/?utm_campaign=in-app&utm_source=addonspage&utm_medium=wordpress-community-events\";s:18:\"featured_image_url\";s:59:\"http://tri.be/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/addon-communty.jpg\";s:11:\"description\";s:393:\"<p>Enable users to submit events to your calendar with Community Events. You can require user accounts or allow visitors to submit without having to have an account. Want to make sure that nothing fishy is going on? Just turn on moderation! Decide if user can edit and manage their own events or simply submit. No scary form setup, just turn it on, configure a few options and off you go.</p>\n\";s:8:\"category\";s:7:\"Premium\";s:11:\"last_update\";N;s:7:\"version\";N;}i:1;O:8:\"stdClass\":7:{s:5:\"title\";s:18:\"Eventbrite Tickets\";s:9:\"permalink\";s:130:\"http://tri.be/shop/wordpress-eventbrite-tickets/?utm_campaign=in-app&utm_source=addonspage&utm_medium=wordpress-eventbrite-tickets\";s:18:\"featured_image_url\";s:62:\"http://tri.be/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/addon-eventbriete.jpg\";s:11:\"description\";s:150:\"<p>The Eventbrite Ticketing Add-On allows you to create &amp; sell tickets directly from the events calendar without leaving the WordPress admin.</p>\n\";s:8:\"category\";s:7:\"Premium\";s:11:\"last_update\";N;s:7:\"version\";N;}i:2;O:8:\"stdClass\":7:{s:5:\"title\";s:19:\"Events Calendar Pro\";s:9:\"permalink\";s:132:\"http://tri.be/shop/wordpress-events-calendar-pro/?utm_campaign=in-app&utm_source=addonspage&utm_medium=wordpress-events-calendar-pro\";s:18:\"featured_image_url\";s:54:\"http://tri.be/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/addon-pro.jpg\";s:11:\"description\";s:665:\"<p><b>An Events Calendar Plugin for People Who Kick Ass</b></p>\n<p>The Events Calendar PRO is a paid Add-On to our open source WordPress plugin <a href=\"/wordpress-events-calendar/\">The Events Calendar.</a> PRO offers a whole host of event management features including recurring events, custom event attributes, saved venues &amp; organizers, venue pages, advanced event admin &amp; lots more.</p>\n<p>Got questions? <a href=\"/support/faqs/\">Read the FAQ</a> or <a href=\"/support/forums/forum/_welcome/pre-sales-questions/\">ask on the forum</a>. Feel free to <a href=\"https://tribe.uservoice.com/forums/195723-feature-ideas\">submit your feature ideas</a>, too.</p>\n\";s:8:\"category\";s:7:\"Premium\";s:11:\"last_update\";N;s:7:\"version\";N;}i:3;O:8:\"stdClass\":7:{s:5:\"title\";s:15:\"Facebook Events\";s:9:\"permalink\";s:104:\"http://tri.be/shop/facebook-events/?utm_campaign=in-app&utm_source=addonspage&utm_medium=facebook-events\";s:18:\"featured_image_url\";s:59:\"http://tri.be/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/addon-facebook.jpg\";s:11:\"description\";s:365:\"<p>With the Facebook Events add-on imported events are manually or automagically created as entries in The Events Calendar. Basic event data along with venue &amp; organizer are populated appropriately. No more entering information in two places, or having to recreate someone else’s listing for a public event you want to include on your WordPress calendar.</p>\n\";s:8:\"category\";s:7:\"Premium\";s:11:\"last_update\";N;s:7:\"version\";N;}i:4;O:8:\"stdClass\":7:{s:5:\"title\";s:19:\"WooCommerce Tickets\";s:9:\"permalink\";s:114:\"http://tri.be/shop/wordpress-wootickets/?utm_campaign=in-app&utm_source=addonspage&utm_medium=wordpress-wootickets\";s:18:\"featured_image_url\";s:54:\"http://tri.be/wp-content/uploads/2013/02/addon-woo.jpg\";s:11:\"description\";s:396:\"<p>With the WooCommerce Tickets add-on for The Events Calendar/Events Calendar PRO, taking control of ticket sales for an upcoming event has never been easier. No third-party websites, no ticket fees…just you, your attendees and one kick ass event. WooCommerce Tickets allows you to add as many tickets as you wish to a given event, and then sell those tickets entirely within your site.</p>\n\";s:8:\"category\";s:7:\"Premiu