 we have had on stage. Folks, young and old, [were] dancing… they had the audience in the palm of their hands!\"</span>\r\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><b><i>- Julia Phillips, Artistic Director, Blue Skies Music Festival (Clarendon, ON)</i></b></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">\"An absolutely riveting experience… pure and radiant talent! The audience response... has been tremendous!\"\r\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><b><i>- Hillary McAndrew-Plate, Senior Manager, Lincoln Center (New York, NY)</i></b></span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">\"They are a force of epic proportion... it is almost impossible to believe that there are only three musicians on stage. Sonic Escape is in the process of becoming an American Treasure.\"\r\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><b><i>- Terry Marshall, Senior Coordinator, Touhill Performing Arts Center (St. Louis, MO)</i></b></span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">\"...opening listeners\' minds to sounds and ideas they\'d never previously considered...\"\r\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><b><i>- Aidan Connolly, Executive Director, Irish Arts Center (New York, NY)</i></b></span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">\"The mastery of the performance was exquisite… together, they became a single body of energy. The impact was huge.\"\r\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><b><i>- Makiko Ishihara, Bits Lounge Magazine (Toronto, ON)</i></b></span></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\">\"I\'ve been to performances all over Europe and America, and I can think of none I\'ve enjoyed more.\"\r\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><b><i>- Bradley Russell, Audience Member (Erie, PA)</i></b>\r\n</span></span>','Quotes/Comments','','publish','closed','open','','quotescomments','','','2014-01-26 22:00:26','2014-01-26 22:00:26','',43,'http://dev.sonicescapemusic.com/?page_id=73',0,'page','',0),(74,1,'2014-01-19 23:45:29','2014-01-19 23:45:29','','Quotes/Comments','','inherit','closed',